Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击准备？难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festum…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你…在那里吗」
