Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.64,1:21:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 就是你
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.53,1:21:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.99,1:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去选择吧 无论多少次
